## DESIGN SYSTEM

### Colors
```
Primary (navy):   #1C2B3A   — authority, calm, trust
Accent (red):     #C8302A   — CTAs, urgency, brand
Warm (cream):     #F7F3EE   — warmth, approachability
Surface:          #FAFAF8   — card backgrounds
Border:           #E5E0D8   — warm dividers
Text:             #2D2D2D   — body copy
Text light:       #6B7280   — captions, meta
White:            #FFFFFF
Footer dark:      #111B26
```

### Typography
```
Display font:  Cormorant Garamond — headlines, heroes, section titles
Body font:     DM Sans — nav, body, CTAs, UI elements

Hero:    clamp(2.6rem, 5.5vw, 4.8rem)
H1:      clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.2rem)
H2:      clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.6rem)
H3:      clamp(1.2rem, 2vw, 1.8rem)
Body:    1.0625rem
Small:   0.875rem
```

### Spacing
```
Max content width: 1200px
Section padding:   96px top/bottom desktop, 56px mobile
Card padding:      28–32px
Border radius:     14px cards, 8px buttons, 100px pills
```

### Shadows
```
Card hover:  0 12px 40px rgba(28,43,58,0.12)
Large:       0 24px 56px rgba(28,43,58,0.16)
Button:      0 8px 20px rgba(200,48,42,0.3)
```

---

## COMPONENT RULES

### Navbar
- White background: `#ffffff`
- Border bottom: `1px solid #E5E0D8`
- Logo: left aligned, height 40px
- Nav links: `#1C2B3A`, hover `#C8302A`
- Phone button: light red bg `rgba(200,48,42,0.08)`, red text `#C8302A`
- Book Consultation: solid red `#C8302A`, white text
- Mobile: hamburger `#1C2B3A`, overlay menu dark navy
- Sticky on scroll

### Footer
- Top band: `#F7F3EE`, 32px padding, logo + tagline + social icons
- Bottom band: `#111B26`, nav columns + contact + copyright
- Logo reads clearly on cream background
- Social icons: SVG, 36px circles, border `1px solid #D1CBC1`

### Buttons
```
Primary:   bg #C8302A, white text, hover #a82520, lift on hover
Secondary: transparent, white text, border rgba(255,255,255,0.3)
Dark:      bg #1C2B3A, white text, hover #0f1a26
Outline:   transparent, navy text/border, hover fills navy
Size:      padding 14px 28px, font-size 15px, font-weight 700
Radius:    8px
```

### Cards
- Background: `#FAFAF8`
- Border: `1px solid #E5E0D8`
- Border radius: 14px
- Hover: lift 3px, red border, red top-bar reveal (scaleX animation)
- Always include: icon + title + description + footer with "Learn More →"

### Service Cards specifically
- Red top border slides in from left on hover (`scaleX(0) → scaleX(1)`)
- Arrow `→` shifts right 4px on hover
- Optional tag pill (e.g. "Most Requested") in top-left

### CTAs
- Every page must end with a CTABlock
- CTABlock: dark navy bg, headline, phone number (large, red), short 4-field form
- Form fields: dark bg inputs with red focus border
- Mobile: sticky 3-button bar (Call / Book / Referral)

### Trust Bar
- Cream background `#F7F3EE`
- 4 items: ⭐ 5.0 Rating · 🏠 Since 2005 · 🩺 Clinical Care · 📞 7 Days
- Font: 13px, 500 weight, navy text
- Appears below hero on homepage and service pages

### Testimonials
- Rotating carousel, 6s interval
- Large quote mark in red (Cormorant Garamond, 72px)
- Quote in display font, italic, navy
- Dot navigation: active dot wider (28px), red

